  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        While all patients with pediatric cardiovascular disease and adults with congenital heart
        disease are of interest, the study will initially focus on four CHD anatomic
        classifications:

          -  Atrial septal defects

          -  Conotruncal abnormalities

          -  Left-sided obstructive lesions

          -  Heterotaxy

        Whenever possible, the study will recruit &quot;trios&quot; of participants--children, mothers and
        fathers-- as well as extended family members when appropriate and feasible.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
